{"type": "article", "id": 2197, "title": "石头法压壶", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:03:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222251tSWcIL8dZYyVjnBG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">不锈钢和耐热玻璃材质的法压壶见惯了，你能想像石头也可以用来做法压壶吗？丹麦设计师 Mette Duedhal 近日就带来了一款以石头作为壶身的法压壶，配以不锈钢的滤压杆和塑料的盖子。这款独特的法压壶摆在厨房里，即便不用来做咖啡，也是不错的摆件。Mette Duedhal 希望这款法压壶在为使用者制作咖啡的同时，也能营造出温暖和舒适的气氛。Stone Push coffee press 于 9 月 5 日在巴黎举行的 </span><a href=\"http://www.maison-objet.com/en\" target=\"_blank\">Maison &amp; Objet 贸易展览会</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">上展出。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261348574EFGlivQXwy39s7C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134857kp1VmJjXUzv49GI8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261348572baY51odChUeXxZ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}